name: Blue Tiles
description: Created December 6th 2020, initially posted to my Instagram @alexradomski. The tiling was created recursively with a maximum depth of 3 (the smallest tile size). Each tile also makes use of perlin noise to create the texture for the tiles. This piece links to Untitled 01 (https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/objkt/35741) which also uses the same algorithm to tile the ASCII characters, and is changed every 30 frames.
